data.description: Updated baths, fresh paint, 2022 heating and cooling and so much more! Covered parking for RV or Trailer, storage shed & your own herb garden! Endless possibilities with the separate large 2 bedroom living area or flex space that could be outfitted as rental apartment, MIL suite, Office etc. NO HOA! Adorable split level home with large wooded lot. This 3bed/2 Full bath home features a white & bright kitchen, spacious living room, homey wood stove fireplace, 3 seasons room overlooking the back yard, hardwoods & tile throughout, larger bedrooms w/walk in closets,
